    "discriminators": [
     "Handling is a quiet, mixed gesture: a soft pickup, some hand friction, a gentle set-down. It shares wood's short ring (decay_time_seconds_60db ~0.1 s) with WOODImpt but at far lower level and crest factor — a set-down is not a hit.",
